{
  "stem": "15938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, every Jewish child to age of 10 was in the same room, in the same class, divided within the class into age groups.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a special-- there was a special building which was one big room [BACKGROUND NOISE] in a very big garden.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably the town, you know, the Jewish people who-- and the boys used to go to the Cheders, so that wasn't such a big problem.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only problem when they started cutting their hair off and peyas off and, you know, and they are abused and so-- it's-- there are some nice memories, till about 1939.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that, I don't even remember anything bad happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just the atmosphere of-- of the life in the town which changed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anxious.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Terribly anxious.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a child you feel the vibration of your parents' anxiety.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shall we go here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shall we go there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Shall we run away?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How can you run away?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where will we run?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it was this kind of all the time and-- and don't stay out late.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if-- and you knew if you were five minutes late, your parents were going mad because they were worried who attacked you on the street.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And to us it's like today, if you can't come home, your mother is worried.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I just thought my mother was worried, but I felt it was more than that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So you know the atmosphere was getting very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, 1942 my father was called up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It wasn't called up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a-- they collected from the town anybody who was anybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Either you were a lawyer or a solicitor or a doctor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They collected all the-- and my-- my father was doing something in the town hall, whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
